title: Hour 3 - NFL Week 4 Preview, Matt Leinart
itunes:title: Hour 3 - NFL Week 4 Preview, Matt Leinart
description:
Dan and the Danettes preview the upcoming weekend in the NFL and former USC and NFL QB Matt Leinart drops by to weigh in on concussions, his days at USC, and Urban Meyer's future coaching prospects.
